main event: A silvery, round object was observed in Lincoln, Nebraska, moving from SW to NE.
interesting points: The object was observed for 15 seconds,It was reported to be the size of a silver dollar,The object was clearly seen to be spinning during the observation,Observers could have mistaken the reflection of the sun off the object's surface, The sighting occurred while observing B-36 aircraft formations.
sighted object: a round silver object in the sky
